Enum BuiltinServerConfiguration

Serializable, Comparable<BuiltinServerConfiguration>
public enum BuiltinServerConfiguration
extends Enum<BuiltinServerConfiguration>

Possible statuses of a built-in server, also called extended function module (EFM), such as a firewall or load balancer (SLB).

In addition to statuses that apply to regular virtual servers, it includes statuses relevant to the upgrade process for functionality of the built-in server.

Author:
Dies Koper
